message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB. The paper focuses on open-domain question answering using both knowledge bases and text, which falls under the intersection of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and database systems (cs.DB) due to its use of knowledge bases.
